title: Jane Eyre (2006) BBC TV
description:
Jane Eyre (2006) is my favorite. I have seen most versions.

Enclosed are the closed captions in a text file for whomever has the time and
ability to create subtitles for this movie. This sort of thing used to be my
speciality, but I'm tired of the tedium. I would guess it would take two weeks at two hours a day to get the job done.

The subtitle files supplied, at first glance, seem to me to be about the same as my closed caption ones. Only one fourth of the movies seems supplied with proper subtitles.
